nce upon a time there lived a monkey in a forest on a tree. There was a crocodile and his wife who lived nearby. The crocodile used to come to the banks to rest. The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile liked the fruits and they became best friends.
The crocodile's wife was not happy with their friendship because the crocodile was speding a lot of time with the monkey
.The crocodile's wife warned the crocodile not to spend too much time with the monkey but the crocdile did not listen to her.The crocodile's wife made a plan to kill the monkey.
But the crocodile got to know about her plan. So he hid the monkey.
